the power for women;

00:01:35.161 --> 00:01:38.064 align:start size:97% position:3%
and that's why the terrorists
are afraid of education.

00:01:38.064 --> 00:01:40.400 align:start size:84% position:16%
They do not want
women to get education

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:44.070 align:start size:88% position:13%
