00:01:52.512 --> 00:01:55.815
When did the Taliban
come to Swat Valley?

00:01:55.815 --> 00:01:58.451 align:start size:84% position:16%
Because before then,
you describe it

00:01:58.451 --> 00:02:00.420
as a paradise, of sorts.

00:02:01.588 --> 00:02:04.157 line:0%
- The Taliban came in
2004, but at that time,

00:02:04.157 --> 00:02:05.058 line:0%
they were quite good.

00:02:05.058 --> 00:02:06.593 line:0%
They did not show their,

00:02:06.593 --> 00:02:08.862 align:start size:84% position:16% line:0%
the terrorism and
they did not blast any

00:02:08.862 --> 00:02:10.396 line:0%
school at that time.

00:02:10.396 --> 00:02:13.466 line:0%
But they started the
real terrorism in 2007.

00:02:13.466 --> 00:02:16.302
They have blasted more
than 400 schools in Swat.

00:02:16.302 --> 00:02:17.437
They have slaughtered people,

00:02:17.437 --> 00:02:20.273
and in the month
of January 2009,

00:02:20.273 --> 00:02:22.408
they used to slaughter
even two, three people

00:02:22.408 --> 00:02:24.878
every night, and they
have flogged women.

00:02:24.878 --> 00:02:26.613
We have seen the
barbaric situation

00:02:26.613 --> 00:02:29.949
of the 21st century,
and we have seen...

00:02:31.351 --> 00:02:34.554 align:start size:97% position:3%
the cruelty, and we have
seen harsh days in our life;

00:02:34.554 --> 00:02:37.690 align:start size:97% position:3%
and those we regarded as the
darkest days of our life.

00:02:37.690 --> 00:02:41.094
So it was really hard
for us at that time.

00:02:41.094 --> 00:02:44.197
- You describe, in the book,

00:02:44.197 --> 00:02:46.032
still, no matter what,

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:50.503 align:start size:84% position:16%
they took the signs
off of schools.

00:02:50.503 --> 00:02:53.039
They went underground.

00:02:53.039 --> 00:02:56.209
But they continued
in the face of--

00:02:56.209 --> 00:03:00.146
You spoke out publicly
against the Taliban.

00:03:00.146 --> 00:03:03.650 align:start size:94% position:6%
What gave you the
courage to continue this?

00:03:04.918 --> 00:03:08.087 line:0%
- You know, my father was great

00:03:08.087 --> 00:03:11.191 line:0%
encouragement for me,
because he spoke of,

00:03:11.191 --> 00:03:12.692 line:0%
he spoke out for women's rights.

00:03:12.692 --> 00:03:14.861 line:0%
He spoke out for
girls' education.

00:03:14.861 --> 00:03:17.430
At that time, I said
that, "Why shall I wait

00:03:17.430 --> 00:03:18.898
"for someone else?

00:03:18.898 --> 00:03:20.934 align:start size:88% position:13%
"Why shall I be looking
to the government,

00:03:20.934 --> 00:03:22.902
"to the army, that
they would help us?

00:03:22.902 --> 00:03:24.737
"Why don't I raise my voice?

00:03:24.737 --> 00:03:27.040
"Why don't we speak
up for our rights?"

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:29.642 align:start size:94% position:6%
The girls of Swat, they
spoke up for their rights.

00:03:29.642 --> 00:03:32.378 align:start size:88% position:13%
I started writing
diary, I spoke on every

00:03:32.378 --> 00:03:35.048 align:start size:97% position:3%
media channel that I could,
and I raised my voice

00:03:35.048 --> 00:03:37.183
on every platform that I could.

00:03:37.183 --> 00:03:39.185
And I said, "I need
to tell the world

00:03:39.185 --> 00:03:40.753
"what is happening in Swat;

00:03:40.753 --> 00:03:42.188 align:start size:84% position:16%
"and I need to
tell the world that

00:03:42.188 --> 00:03:44.023 align:start size:81% position:19%
"Swat is suffering
from terrorism,

00:03:44.023 --> 00:03:46.659
"and we need to fight
against terrorism."

00:03:46.659 --> 00:03:48.761
- When did you realize...

00:03:50.163 --> 00:03:52.999 align:start size:81% position:19%
the Taliban had
made you a target?

00:03:55.868 --> 00:03:58.037
- When, in 2012, we were--

00:03:59.372 --> 00:04:00.807 align:start size:84% position:16%
I was with my father,
and someone came,

00:04:00.807 --> 00:04:04.110 align:start size:88% position:13%
and she told us that,
"Have you seen on Google

00:04:04.110 --> 00:04:06.179
"that if you search your name,

00:04:06.179 --> 00:04:07.947
"the Taliban have
threatened you?"

00:04:07.947 --> 00:04:09.682
And I just could not believe it.

00:04:09.682 --> 00:04:11.651
I said, "No, it's not true."

00:04:11.651 --> 00:04:14.020 align:start size:88% position:13%
And even after that
threat, when we saw it,

00:04:14.020 --> 00:04:16.155 align:start size:88% position:13%
I was not worried
about myself that much.

00:04:16.155 --> 00:04:17.857
I was worried about my father,

00:04:17.857 --> 00:04:20.126 align:start size:88% position:13%
because we thought that
the Taliban are not

00:04:20.126 --> 00:04:22.829 align:start size:88% position:13%
that much cruel, that
they would kill a child,

00:04:22.829 --> 00:04:25.031
because I was 14 at that time.

00:04:25.031 --> 00:04:27.867
But then later on,
I used to start--

00:04:27.867 --> 00:04:29.702
I started thinking about that,

00:04:29.702 --> 00:04:31.471 align:start size:84% position:16%
and I used to think
that the Talib

00:04:31.471 --> 00:04:34.574
would come, and he
would just kill me.

00:04:34.574 --> 00:04:36.009
But then I said, "If he comes,

00:04:36.009 --> 00:04:38.611
"what would you do, Malala?"

00:04:38.611 --> 00:04:40.446
Then I would reply myself that,

00:04:40.446 --> 00:04:42.348
"Malala, just take
a shoe and hit him;"

00:04:42.348 --> 00:04:45.685
but then I said... (laughter)

00:04:45.685 --> 00:04:47.420
But then I said,
"If you hit a Talib

00:04:47.420 --> 00:04:48.855
"with your shoe,
then there would be

00:04:48.855 --> 00:04:51.591 align:start size:84% position:16%
"no difference between
you and the Talib.

00:04:51.591 --> 00:04:53.926
"You must not treat
others that much

00:04:53.926 --> 00:04:56.162
"with cruelty, and
that much harshly.

00:04:56.162 --> 00:04:58.665 align:start size:88% position:13%
"You must fight others,
but through peace

00:04:58.665 --> 00:05:00.533
"and through dialogue,
and through education."

00:05:00.533 --> 00:05:02.669 align:start size:84% position:16%
Then I said, "I'll
tell him how important

00:05:02.669 --> 00:05:04.904
"education is, and
that I even want

00:05:04.904 --> 00:05:07.507
"education for your
children as well;"

00:05:07.507 --> 00:05:10.076 align:start size:97% position:3%
and I would tell him, "that's
what I want to tell you.

00:05:10.076 --> 00:05:11.811
"Now do what you want."

00:05:11.811 --> 00:05:15.915
(audience applause and cheering)

